Onyeisiala Muhammadu Buhari emeela Usman Alkali Baba onyeisi ndị uweojii Naịjiria ọhụrụ.
Ozi si n'aka minista na-ahụ maka ndị uweojii bụ Maigari Dingyadi pụta n'Abuja taa (06/04/2021) gbara ama na ọ malitere ọrụ ozigbo.

Ị chọrọ ịbụ onye uweojii? Lekwa usoro ndenye aha ọhụrụ
Agbanweela onyeisi ndị uweojii na Rivers State
Onyeisiala Buharị agbatịala oge ọrụ IGP Mohammed Adamu ruo ọnwa atọ
Baba na-anọchi Mohammed Adamu bụ onye e sepụrụ oche n'otele dịka ọ gara njem ọrụ n'Owerri.
Alkali Baba bụbu osote onyeisi ndị uweojii tupu e nye ya ọkwa ọhụrụ a ka ọ malitere ozigbo.
A mụrụ ya afọ 1963 na state Yobe.
Ọ gara ụlọakwụkwọ dị elu na mahadum 'Bayero University  Kano' nakwa  Usman Dan Fodio University dị na Maiduguri.
O sonyere ụlọọrụ ndi uweoji na afọ 1988.
Usman Alkali Baba nwere nzere Masters na agụmakwụkwọ Public Administration nakwa Political Science .
O so n' otu ndi gụrụ n'ụlọakwụkwọ 'National Defence College'  nakwa otu 'International Association of Chiefs of Police.
Ọ bụbu onyeisi ndi uweojii Zone 7 Markudi na Zone 7 Abuja ma bụrụkwa onye kọmishọna ndi uweojii n' Abuja nakwa Delta steeti.
Nwafọ Yobe steeti, Baba rụkwara ọrụ dika onye odeakwụkwọ ndi uweojii  tupu a họpụta ya dika Osote Onyeisi gburugburu(AIG) ndi uweojii n' abalị atọ nke ọnwa Nọvemba 2020.
Gọvanọ Rivas steeti bụ Nyesom Wike kwuru okwu n'ige TV n'ehihie Fraịde nke mere ka onye ọbụla kpụrụ ya n'ọnụ.
